  "detailed_description": "Explore a weird casino, build your slot machine and punch enemies in the face!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239800/extras/4fb70a3191cc0a0b17b6981c1b3ce2fd.poster.avif?t=1769185018\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239800/extras/4fb70a3191cc0a0b17b6981c1b3ce2fd.webm?t=1769185018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239800/extras/4fb70a3191cc0a0b17b6981c1b3ce2fd.mp4?t=1769185018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>One Armed Bandit is a \"deck\"-building roguelite where your combat actions are determined by the outcome of your (manually stopped) slot machine. Add more symbols to the machine to build incredible combos, get more items to grow stronger, play gambly minigames to get more stuff. <br>Don't mess around for too long, the bouncers are coming to get you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239800/extras/1b1888b9cb8464ce3311aa609a6d251c.poster.avif?t=1769185018\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239800/extras/1b1888b9cb8464ce3311aa609a6d251c.webm?t=1769185018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239800/extras/1b1888b9cb8464ce3311aa609a6d251c.mp4?t=1769185018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique slot-machine based combat<br></li><li>100 symbols to combo with each other<br></li><li>Randomized map for a fresh challenge every time<br></li><li>3 minigames to waste your money on<br></li><li>Dozens of enemies<br></li><li>Flexible difficulty settings<br></li><li>Excessive gambling and alcohol consumption</li></ul><br>Remember, the house always wins!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239800/extras/255ebb2e684307a367914b80be845550.avif?t=1769185018\" width=616 height=347 /></span>",
